    "Id": "vehicledef_EPONA-PRIME",
    "Name": "Epona Pursuit Tank",
    "UIName": "Epona Pursuit Tank PRIME",
    "Details": "<b>Name: <color=#85DBF6>Epona Pursuit Tank Prime</color>\nArmor: <color=#85DBF6>Ferro-Fibrous</color>\tTechnology: <color=#85DBF6>Clan</color>\nMovement: <color=#85DBF6>9/14 (Hover)</color>\tEngine: <color=#85DBF6>215 Fusion</color></b>\n\nThe Epona Pursuit Tank was once a front-line unit in the most prestigious Galaxies of the Horses. Known for its speed and scouting capabilities, it is built on the largest hovercraft frame possible, reaching 150 km/h at the expense of armor.\n\nThe primary configuration of the Epona is meant for close-quarters combat. Four Medium Pulse Lasers provide accurate damage that even most 'Mechs will have to worry about. A Streak SRM-4 enables the Epona to act as a vehicle-killer and to damage exposed critical systems. All of the armament is located in the vehicle's turret.",
